  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="31590412">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Janedlj/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2289866-43.jpg" alt="海狸君" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31590412/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31590412/" class="">第256页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Janedlj/" class=" " title="海狸君">海狸君</a>
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31590412">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">世上好多事都只差个耐烦地等待而误了自己。人，从小就要锻炼等待，要耐烦，要乖乖地看别人骑车子，舞关刀，打圈圈......我这是真话，你要信。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-05-13 23:04</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                世上好多事都只差个耐烦地等待而误了自己。人，从小就要锻炼等待，要耐烦，要乖乖地看别人骑车子，舞关刀，打圈圈......我这是真话，你要信。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

